<p class="definition" data-word = "The Law of Universal Gravitation">
    Any two masses, anywhere in the universe, are attracted to each other by this formula:
</p>
<p class="equation">
    $$
    F_g = G \frac{m_1 m_2}{d^2}
    $$
</p>

